  "comment": "StarColor360 Wash Light 24x 15W RGBWA Outdoor: The StarColor360 is a professional LED Architectural projector, designed for refined wall-washing, compatible for both architectural and entertainment applications. This impressive and robust high power LED fixture is IP66 rated and hence for outdoor and indoor use. The construction of the chassis is die-cast aluminum and tempered glass with no usage of fans for ventilation. Ready-made flightcases are also available! (for safe transport)",
